# Supabase CLI Invocation

When running Supabase CLI commands in this workspace:

- Always use `npx supabase ...` instead of `supabase ...`.
- Applies to deploy, migrations, linking, and local function operations.
- Example: `npx supabase functions deploy <function-name>`.
